  "title": "Admin Assistant / Receptionist",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:</p><p>We are looking for a friendly and organized Admin Assistant/Receptionist to join us! This role is perfect for someone who enjoys working in a dynamic environment, interacting with different people like parents, children and package holders and keeping things running smoothly.</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>Greet and assist students, parents, and visitors</p><p>Handle phone calls/whatsapp, emails, and inquiries</p><p>Manage class schedules and registrations</p><p>Process payments and maintain records</p><p>Assist with basic admin tasks and company organization</p><p>Support coaches and staff with day-to-day operations</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Must be willing to work over the weekends</p><p>Must be available to commit to extended working hours during scheduled events(involves packing/unpacking).</p><p>Strong communication and customer service skills</p><p>Basic computer proficiency (Microsoft Office, booking software is a plus)</p><p>Organized, detail-oriented, and able to multitask</p><p>Able to perform ad-hoc duties as necessary</p><p>Friendly and professional demeanor</p><p>Prior admin or receptionist experience is a bonus but not required</p>",
